        <title>SPFE Development Tasks</title>
        <understanding><p>If you have successfully completed the steps in <task>getting started</task>, you are now ready to create your own documents using the SPFE build system. You need to perform the following tasks:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p><task>Create the SFPE configuration file</task></p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p><task>Add a topic-set</task></p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p><task>Add a topic</task></p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p><task>Add a doc-set</task></p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>You may also want to <task>customize build system</task></p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </understanding>
